<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Login OTP</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #121212;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }
    .email-container {
      background-color: #1e1e1e;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .email-container h1 {
      color: #1DB954;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .email-container h2 {
      color: #FFFFFF;
      font-size: 48px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .email-container p {
      color: #B3B3B3;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .otp-code {
      background-color: #1DB954;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      color: #121212;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 36px;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #B3B3B3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <h1>Here is Your OTP for Login</h1>
    <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
    <p>Use this code to complete your login process.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you for choosing our service!<br> Stay secure, stay safe.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>